00:23:51.805 --> 00:23:54.030 align:middle line:90%


00:23:54.030 --> 00:23:59.190 align:middle line:84%
Imagine what it would be like to
be God, resting in a perfectly

00:23:59.190 --> 00:24:03.460 align:middle line:84%
blissful, overwhelmingly
peaceful state of being

