In that profound stillness,
nothing is missing.

00:24:18.160 --> 00:24:20.070 align:middle line:90%


00:24:20.070 --> 00:24:22.975 align:middle line:84%
And there is no
desire whatsoever.

00:24:22.975 --> 00:24:27.700 align:middle line:90%


00:24:27.700 --> 00:24:29.687 align:middle line:90%
Absolutely nothing has occurred.

00:24:29.687 --> 00:24:32.370 align:middle line:90%


00:24:32.370 --> 00:24:39.110 align:middle line:84%
That's where you were before the
beginning, before the Big Bang.

00:24:39.110 --> 00:24:42.130 align:middle line:90%


00:24:42.130 --> 00:24:45.695 align:middle line:84%
Perfect peace and
boundless bliss.

00:24:45.695 --> 00:24:48.180 align:middle line:90%


00:24:48.180 --> 00:24:51.505 align:middle line:90%
Quietude without end.

00:24:51.505 --> 00:24:54.890 align:middle line:90%


00:24:54.890 --> 00:24:57.830 align:middle line:84%
Unburdened by the
weight of existence,

00:24:57.830 --> 00:25:00.411 align:middle line:84%
you could not have
been more content.

00:25:00.411 --> 00:25:08.110 align:middle line:90%


00:25:08.110 --> 00:25:15.300 align:middle line:84%
Yet, for some reason, out
of that perfect contentment

00:25:15.300 --> 00:25:17.635 align:middle line:84%
you made a decision
to create the cosmos.

00:25:17.635 --> 00:25:20.640 align:middle line:90%


00:25:20.640 --> 00:25:23.830 align:middle line:84%
You chose to manifest
a material universe

00:25:23.830 --> 00:25:25.840 align:middle line:84%
from your own
unmanifest emptiness.

00:25:25.840 --> 00:25:28.400 align:middle line:90%


00:25:28.400 --> 00:25:30.560 align:middle line:84%
You could have continued
to rest happily

00:25:30.560 --> 00:25:33.290 align:middle line:84%
in being, meditating
on nothingness

00:25:33.290 --> 00:25:36.895 align:middle line:84%
for more countless eons
of infinite no time.

00:25:36.895 --> 00:25:38.460 align:middle line:90%


00:25:38.460 --> 00:25:41.932 align:middle line:84%
But you had already
done that forever.

00:25:41.932 --> 00:25:47.080 align:middle line:90%


00:25:47.080 --> 00:25:51.630 align:middle line:84%
So you chose to take the
unthinkable step and endeavour

00:25:51.630 --> 00:25:55.912 align:middle line:84%
to manifest your own
self in and through form.

00:25:55.912 --> 00:25:59.356 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:25:59.356 --> 00:26:05.260 align:middle line:90%


