00:26:11.610 --> 00:26:16.780 align:middle line:84%
arise to do something so vast,
so complex, so overwhelming?

00:26:16.780 --> 00:26:18.400 align:middle line:90%


00:26:18.400 --> 00:26:19.910 align:middle line:84%
What could be a
greater challenge

00:26:19.910 --> 00:26:24.760 align:middle line:84%
than to create something out of
