00:26:24.760 --> 00:26:27.825 align:middle line:84%
universe before form
had never existed?

00:26:27.825 --> 00:26:30.890 align:middle line:90%


00:26:30.890 --> 00:26:34.100 align:middle line:84%
But you apparently decided to
take that unimaginable step.

00:26:34.100 --> 00:26:35.390 align:middle line:90%


